---
title: Grilled Roman-Style Chicken with Tomato and Herb Salad
description: This Italian-inspired dish is a light meal, perfect for those hot summer nights. Dig in to juicy marinated chicken, grilled tomatoes, ciabatta, fresh torn basil and a sprinkling of Parmesan. That's amore!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/poulet-grille-a-la-romaine-1f9366eb.jpg
